# Deadline picker
<LEADER>oid

# Deadline format
DEADLINE:<2025-06-05>

# Deadline with repeater
DEADLINE:<2025-06-05 +1d>
Repeats
Daily 1d
Weekly 1w
Monthly 1m
Yearly 1y

Optional warning period after repeater
DEADLINE:<2025-06-05 +1m -3d>


